    "description": {
      "zh": "跳蚤市场: 59,289₽ | 物品价值: 89,700 | Therapist报价: 56,511₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 116,610₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级2 < 81,240₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级1 < Alyonka x3 + 药 x1 | Σ ≈ 103,540₽\n\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > Assessment - Part 3 @ Mechanic\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > First in Line @ Therapist\n任务需要 x8 > Get a Foothold @ Skier\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > Narcotic - Part 4 @ 莲花\n\n专为特种部队人员定制。它能够在短时间内降低体温，显著减缓代谢。使用SJ9可以显著减少向周围环境散发的热量，同时保持在体内新陈代谢的安全水平上。它被用于夜间行动，让人体在热成像仪器下几乎不可见。",
      "en": "跳蚤市场: 59,289₽ | 物品价值: 89,700 | Therapist报价: 56,511₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 116,610₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级2 < 81,240₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级1 < Alyonka x3 + 药 x1 | Σ ≈ 103,540₽\n\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > Assessment - Part 3 @ Mechanic\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > First in Line @ Therapist\n任务需要 x8 > Get a Foothold @ Skier\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > Narcotic - Part 4 @ 莲花\n\nDesigned for special forces personnel. It makes it possible to reduce the human body temperature for a short time, significantly slowing down the metabolism. The use of SJ9 leads to a significant reduction in the amount of heat released into the environment, while maintaining a safe level of metabolism inside. It is used during night operations, allowing to be hardly visible for thermal imaging devices."
    },
